activities:
Outscale Inc. receives, collects, held and/or process personal data regarding individuals located in the EEA and/or Switzerland (“EEA and Swiss data subjects”) for different purposes such as:
- Managing sales and marketing to individuals, consumers and/or businesses;
- Effecting transactions with individuals, consumers and/or businesses; 
- Supplying services and/or products to individuals, consumers and/or businesses, including services that provide computing and various information processing services; 
- Operating, personalizing, developing and improving Outscale Inc. services and products; 
- Providing customer sales and technical support and/or customer relationship management; 
- Managing relations with suppliers; 
- Complying with governmental, legislative and regulatory bodies; 
- Managing financial and billing process. 

The personal data received by Outscale Inc. from EEA and/or Switzerland includes both personal data that Outscale Inc. processes as a data controller and personal data that Outscale Inc. processes as a data processor.
